{"tid":892204,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實成日見d人講樓價，究竟有無人真係認真研究過發生乜事","createTime":"2018-11-06T16:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T16:41:57.000Z","uid":35870,"like":9,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"10d140fe3d047711de1c6ecd0da28f3b1fbd381d","tid":892204,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"就好似近排個樓價跌市，成班衝出黎係到又咩淡淡租租供供，真係心諗做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實求撚其search下都會見到有人做過研究架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過當然，好多人一句:<br />\nd專家食屎啦/經濟學太多assumption<br />\n跟住就完全無深入探討過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實想講下HKMA呢篇嘅research，2017年出嘅<br />\nEstimating the Drivers of Hong Kong' Housing Price: Short Run Dynamic<br />\n<br />\nTommy Wong, Ken Wong, Michael Cheng<br />\n<br />\n其實已經好簡單指出左，香港樓價係short run係受到以下factors影響:<br />\nBank credit supply <br />\nHousing Supply<br />\nMortgage rate<br />\nHousing Demand<br />\nMarket Sentiment<br />\n<br />\n5個factors近排都中左幾樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家嘅討論可唔可以學術少少，高質少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到成班人衝出黎互相binc<br />\n屌！咁個市一係升一係跌架啦，係到互相binc無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8361ea2a9d4069eed9b044251cd4627f6cbf70","tid":892204,"uid":13724,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"有人認為housing demand 壓到一切吖嘛，有乜好討論"},{"pid":"fd1ef7996a3c1407098c109241a6850037b523b1","tid":892204,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea8361ea2a9d4069eed9b044251cd4627f6cbf70","tid":892204,"uid":13724,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"有人認為housing demand 壓到一切吖嘛，有乜好討論"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T17:23:21.000Z","msg":"廿鳩幾萬份居屋伸請表，一抽完抽唔中就出私人市場搶樓，<br />\n<br />\n不過居屋政策打後年年都有5000伙供應，唔係得一年"},{"pid":"c25a0225761726de69bb70871d06ccdfee7cba89","tid":892204,"uid":37599,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"10d140fe3d047711de1c6ecd0da28f3b1fbd381d","tid":892204,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"就好似近排個樓價跌市，成班衝出黎係到又咩淡淡租租供供，真係心諗做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實求撚其search下都會見到有人做過研究架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過當然，好多人一句:<br />\nd專家食屎啦/經濟學太多assumption<br />\n跟住就完全無深入探討過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實想講下HKMA呢篇嘅research，2017年出嘅<br />\nEstimating the Drivers of Hong Kong' Housing Price: Short Run Dynamic<br />\n<br />\nTommy Wong, Ken Wong, Michael Cheng<br />\n<br />\n其實已經好簡單指出左，香港樓價係short run係受到以下factors影響:<br />\nBank credit supply <br />\nHousing Supply<br />\nMortgage rate<br />\nHousing Demand<br />\nMarket Sentiment<br />\n<br />\n5個factors近排都中左幾樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家嘅討論可唔可以學術少少，高質少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到成班人衝出黎互相binc<br />\n屌！咁個市一係升一係跌架啦，係到互相binc無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T22:37:24.000Z","msg":"其實五隻字已經可以summarize d專家所講既factor<br />\n<br />\n阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab00d9c0b8a3ed578da2fabbc17752ef18095e7","tid":892204,"uid":10101,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T22:51:15.000Z","msg":"成日講剛需，宜家啲剛需呢？<br />\n根本買樓係解決投資需求，唔係解決自住需求，自住需求如果真係咁多，就周街都有人訓街啦<br />\n一跌就無人買啦，香港人點會咁蠢，高追一件會貶值既貨品。但如果今日買完，聽日都會升值，傻既都會去買<br />\n<br />\n實有人狗衝出來講，香港樓長遠一定升，你睇之前點點點<br />\n但成日都講，投資表現不能用過去表現來保證，環境係會轉，邊個可以話我知，騰迅可以上返480蚊，或者可以既，20年後啦，但中間發生幾多事，又有幾多更賺錢既投資項目，一定唔係得買樓咁單一，輸左機會成本囉"},{"pid":"7cd08473d65ff9cac5f48196f5c4bbb963e9a6a9","tid":892204,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T22:53:22.000Z","msg":"李十X買個時係升<br />\n李十X賣個時係跌<br />\n<br />\n財經台班aa9IT9入貨時係跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例子：劏房狗3zero，core窿王青山道，摸頂俠AA9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69f133ccbe2135f25497d729156f19034be789d","tid":892204,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd1ef7996a3c1407098c109241a6850037b523b1","tid":892204,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea8361ea2a9d4069eed9b044251cd4627f6cbf70","tid":892204,"uid":13724,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"有人認為housing demand 壓到一切吖嘛，有乜好討論"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T17:23:21.000Z","msg":"廿鳩幾萬份居屋伸請表，一抽完抽唔中就出私人市場搶樓，<br />\n<br />\n不過居屋政策打後年年都有5000伙供應，唔係得一年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"居屋仲要好多人係9抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0630ab9004165dea2022f23fa13442bdfbe489e3","tid":892204,"uid":56501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:26: